text.tspan: *Tip: This organization is your Spacewalk's default organization. Entitlements for this organization are linked to your Spacewalk certificate file, so they are not
modifiable. If you remove entitlements from a non-default organization above, those entitlements will be added back to the default organization, and if you
add entitlements from a non-default organization they will be deducted from the default organization.
